      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box aw-briefly\">\n\t\t\t我不推荐楼主移民去巴基斯坦，但我首先要把它的优点罗列一下，好让你不后悔：<br/>\n巴基斯坦是一个物价很低的国家，尽管人们的收入也很低。2元人民币等值的金额就能买到一大盘羊肉手抓饭，1元人民币买一大杯奶茶，2.5元人民币让你坐出租车一公里左右（大城市）。<br/>\n在这个视频里，你可以有一个直观的认识：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj14LTEwcVk0MEhrVQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x-10qY40HkU\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x-10qY40HkU</a><br/>\n巴基斯坦也有些现代化的享受设施，像是西餐厅（对了，他们叫西餐western food，他们看待西方事物的好奇如同中国人）、星巴克、现代化的购物中心、豪华酒店和类似的东西，价格当然远远低于中国或更富有的国家。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2M1YjhjODJmMDkzNjUyNmM1MzdlLnBuZz93aWR0aD03ODAmaGVpZ2h0PTQyNw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7c5b8c82f0936526c537e.png?width=780&amp;height=427\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7c5b8c82f0936526c537e.png?width=780&amp;height=427\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7c5b8c82f0936526c537e.png?width=780&amp;height=427\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n全世界的星巴克、UNIQLO、MUJI都是差不多的，不仅是巴基斯坦、印度这种南亚有，很多非洲国家、中亚、中东国家都有，可以说墙内人赖以骄傲的“大城市风格”在国际上没什么稀奇的，这就是个模板而已。<br/>\n-------<br/>\n以上都是物质层面的介绍，但是我不推荐楼主移民巴基斯坦，以下是原因：<br/>\n1，巴基斯坦在经济学人的民主指数上显示为3.25分，是一个独裁国家，就算你再富有，也不可能拥有尊严的。如果你移民到那个地方，你将要给独裁者交税，为虎作伥。<br/>\n2，巴基斯坦在族裔平等、LGBT+权益、宗教自由和劳工权益上非常糟糕，有着多次的侵犯人权记录，不仅是政府有系统性的对弱势群体迫害，民间也存在大量私刑。在不自由的天空下你只能呼吸不自由的空气，除非你像牲口一样只关心吃饱喝足，你无法在当地感受到自由。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGQxYjZjMmQwNTg4ODM3Y2VjYTAwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNjM5JmhlaWdodD04Mzc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0d1b6c2d0588837ceca00.png?width=1639&amp;height=837\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0d1b6c2d0588837ceca00.png?width=1639&amp;height=837\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0d1b6c2d0588837ceca00.png?width=1639&amp;height=837\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n3，巴基斯坦有网络封锁，翻墙同样是违法的。你在中国已经承受过了没有国际互联网的时光，没有必要再接受一次。以下内容来自德国之音及路透社：<br/>\n<blockquote>In October 2020 Government of Pakistan issued new policy rules called Citizens Protection (Against Online Harm) Rules 2020 or the Removal and Blocking of Unlawful Content (Procedure, Oversight and Safeguards) under 2016 Prevention of Electronic Crimes Act (PECA).<br/>\nThe government of Pakistan intends to access internet user data and control and remove objectionable content. The companies would be required to remove or block any asked content from their websites within 24 hours after being reported by Pakistani authorities, social media companies or internet service providers face may be fined of up to $3.14 million (€2.57 million) for failure to curb the sharing of content deemed to be defamatory of Islam, promoting terrorism, hate speech, pornography or any content viewed as problematic to Pakistan's national security.<br/>\nRights activists complain that new rules are compromising user privacy at mercy of Pakistani establishment sans judicial oversight, likely to erode media freedom and freedom of expression further there by erode political freedoms and result in increased censorship.<br/>\nSince then, dating apps like Tinder are banned in Pakistan, video sharing app named TikTok faced a temporary ban til removed content; issued notices to U.S.A. based Ahmadiyya community web portal TrueIslam.com, Google and Wikipedia for returning search results displaying Ahmadiyya community and their leadership, Mirza Masroor Ahmad, 's claims of Muslimness.</blockquote><br/>\n根据维基百科，以下网站在巴基斯坦是曾经部分时间或至今仍被禁止的：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTIxNmJiMzMwZjRlNmFjZjdhMTllLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMTk3JmhlaWdodD0xNDIy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a216bb330f4e6acf7a19e.png?width=1197&amp;height=1422\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a216bb330f4e6acf7a19e.png?width=1197&amp;height=1422\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a216bb330f4e6acf7a19e.png?width=1197&amp;height=1422\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n4（Bonus），巴基斯坦的英语并非通用，你很难听懂当地口音的英语，如果你有自信，以下是一个听力测试：<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1XWHRSdkE2VmFJTQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WXtRvA6VaIM\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WXtRvA6VaIM</a> <div class=\"aw-stretch-content-button-container\"><button class=\"aw-stretch-content-button\" type=\"button\"></button></div></div>",
